            </ul>
        </div>
        
        <div class="warning-box">
            <span class="icon">🎯</span>
            <strong>CRITICAL FOR CONSISTENCY:</strong><br>
            Every prompt in this guide = [Master DNA Prompt] + [Specific Scenario] + [Attach Reference Face Image]<br><br>
            This triple combination guarantees your AI influencer looks identical in every photo.
        </div>
        
        <p class="intro-text" style="margin-top: 30px; font-weight: 600;">
            Ready? Let's create your 100 professional images. Turn to the next page.
