            <h2 class="page-title">THE 100 PROMPTS</h2>
        </div>
        
        <p class="intro-text">
            Each prompt below follows the same structure. Here's how to use them:
        </p>
        
        <div class="tips-box">
            <h3>Prompt Usage Instructions:</h3>
            <ul>
                <li><strong>Replace [MASTER DNA]</strong> with your actual Master DNA Prompt from Step 1</li>
                <li><strong>Attach your Reference Face image</strong> when generating (critical for consistency)</li>
                <li><strong>Copy prompts exactly</strong> - every word matters for quality</li>
                <li><strong>Generate 2-3 variations</strong> of each prompt, pick the best result</li>
