                ---<br>
                [YOUR MASTER DNA PROMPT HERE] + Professional headshot photography, Canon EOS R5, 85mm f/1.8 lens, soft studio lighting with key light at 45 degrees, neutral expression, direct eye contact with camera, shoulders square to camera, clean white background, sharp focus on eyes, shallow depth of field, professional corporate style. 8K resolution, photorealistic, commercial photography quality, color graded.<br>
                ---<br>
